videos.description: Ohio State's Kaleb Wesson gets position in the post and uses an up-and-under move to draw a foul and bank home the shot.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Buckeyes' bench fired up over Wesson's and-1) 2020/02/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Buckeyes' bench fired up over Wesson's and-1

videos.description: Ohio State's CJ Walker grabs a rebound on defense and goes coast-to-coast, finishing in transition with a sweet Eurostep.

videos.headline: Walker Eurosteps past Maryland defense

videos.description: Andre Wesson gets the ball in the middle of the Maryland zone and zips a pass under the basket to his brother, Kaleb, for the two-handed jam.
